@startuml
!include ../plantuml-theme.iuml
hide methods
hide stereotypes
left to right direction

title 图 3.8 系统 E-R 图（PlantUML 初稿）

class "users" as Users {
  +id
  --
  username
  role
  org_tags
  primary_org
}

class "organization_tags" as OrgTags {
  +tag_id
  --
  name
  parent_tag
  created_by
}

class "file_upload" as FileUpload {
  +file_md5
  --
  file_name
  user_id
  org_tag
  is_public
  status
  sensitivity_level
  sensitive_types
}

class "chunk_info" as ChunkInfo {
  +file_md5
  +chunk_index
  --
  chunk_md5
  storage_path
}

class "document_vectors" as DocumentVectors {
  +vector_id
  --
  file_md5
  chunk_id
  text_content
  safe_text_content
  normalized_text_content
  is_restricted
  external_model_allowed
  sensitivity_level
}

Users "1" --> "0..*" FileUpload : uploads
OrgTags "1" --> "0..*" FileUpload : org_tag
Users "1" --> "0..*" OrgTags : created_by
FileUpload "1" --> "0..*" ChunkInfo : has chunks
FileUpload "1" --> "0..*" DocumentVectors : has blocks
OrgTags "0..1" --> "0..*" OrgTags : parent_tag
OrgTags "1" --> "0..*" Users : primary_org

legend bottom
如果终稿必须使用严格的 Crow's Foot 样式，
建议你在 draw.io 中按此结构人工重画一次。
但从语义和字段关系上，这份 PlantUML 初稿已经可以直接用。
endlegend
@enduml
